#: ../../source/faqs.md:236
msgid ""
"On a separate host machine (e.g., a standard Ubuntu server), pull the "
"image for the target ARM64 architecture and package it into a `.tar` "
"file."
msgstr "在另一台宿主机（如标准的 Ubuntu 服务器）上，拉取目标 ARM64 架构的镜像并打包为 `.tar` 文件。"

